   new business ideas
   pictures of a person mailing a letter and a person using a computer
   visionary. imaginative. resourceful. The u s p s is interested in
   visionary business ideas and proposals that will help us continue to
   deliver quality services in the twenty first century.
    To submit an innovative business proposal to USPS Corporate and
   Business Development, click submit idea.
   submit idea
    Information regarding the process for submitting suggestions for Stamp
   subjects and designs, click more info.
   more info
    To get information on making an unsolicited proposal to USPS
   Purchasing and Materials, click more info.
   more info

   An unsolicited proposal is an offer to sell to the USPS the rights to
   ideas, concepts, products, processes, or technology. This program is
   managed by USPS Purchasing and Materials.

